      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, and the interior upholstery exhibits significant wear and some staining. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but the suspension is starting to feel loose and it will likely need new brakes in the near future. It is a solid candidate for someone willing to put in a little work to bring it back to its best.",
