      "description": "Hey everyone! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just left the dealership! It's been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless. It drives like a total dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
