    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 that defines mechanical perfection. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained Double-VANOS system for optimal valve timing. The chassis integrity is flawless, with a documented subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring maximum longitudinal traction. Every fluid line, heat shield, and fastener reflects a factory-fresh state. This is a rare, turn-key opportunity for a purist seeking a benchmark-level driving machine.",
