    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and feels as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior features flawless factory paint with a deep, mirror-like finish, protected by a professional ceramic coating; you will find no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections of any kind. The wheels are pristine with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-full tread. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather seats are supple and free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the dash and trim pieces are devoid of any scratches or sun fading. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium infotainment system, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is in peak condition with a full, documented service history from authorized dealerships. It drives tight and responsive, with smooth shifts and a powerful, quiet engine. This sale includes all original keys, the window sticker, complete owner's manuals, and a custom-fit indoor car cover. This is an uncompromising example for a buyer who demands perfection.",
